org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.matching.common.query.postprocessing.transformation

Class Subsumption

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.matching.common.query.postprocessing.transformation.Subsumption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryTransformation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SyntacticSubsumption, TemporalSubsumption

    public abstract class Subsumption
extends Object
implements QueryTransformation
    Abstract base class for subsumptions of clauses. A simplifying assumption is made: smaller clauses are not subsumed by larger ones. It is not guaranteed that all subsumptions or the optimal sequence of subsumptions are applied
